SP / 11 / 12.9 / 7 / 63.6
Total / 85 / 100.0 / 34 / 40.0
[Source: Sistema de Vigilancia em Saude, Ministerio da Saude (SVS/MS)
(System of Health Surveillance, Ministry of Health, Brazil).]
(*) preliminary data
